@EventReservation.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5009

### Registrar novo usuário
POST {{EventReservation.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Joăo Silva",
  "email": "joao@teste.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Login
POST {{EventReservation.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@teste.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}